    public class BoundedList<K>
extends java.util.LinkedList<K>
    a class which is a like linkedlist bounded by a maximum length
    only the add method enforces the limit - the others are seen just through inheritance!
    used inheritance in lieu of encapsulation because this list needs to be iterated by JSP files repeatedly-inserted elements are moved to front, the bottom is lost to make place
